### Event Manager API - JetBrains HTTP Client
### Make sure your Spring Boot application is running on localhost:8080

### Variables
@baseUrl = localhost:8080
@eventId = 123abc
@participantId = 456def

### 1. Listar próximos eventos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Accept: application/json

### 2. Obter evento específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/{{eventId}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Obter evento específico com lista de participantes (como organizador)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/{{eventId}}?participantId={{participantId}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. Criar novo evento - Workshop
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantName": "João Silva",
  "participantEmail": "joao@email.com",
  "name": "Workshop de Spring Boot",
  "description": "Aprenda os conceitos básicos do Spring Boot",
  "date": "2024-12-15",
  "slots": 50,
  "location": "Auditório Principal - São Luís/MA"
}

