### 10. Buscar participantes por IDs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/participants?ids=456def,789ghi,012jkl
Accept: application/json

### 11. Buscar participantes por IDs (formato alternativo)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/participants?ids=abc123&ids=def456&ids=ghi789
Accept: application/json

